scene.message:
Maki: You've got business with{nl}
the doctor?{wait_fr:32} Hey, let's get{nl}
out of a place like this...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Do we really have to{nl}
go to the abandoned factory?{waitkey}A grimy place like that just{nl}
doesn't suit a guy like me!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Do we really have to{nl}
beat Kandori?{waitkey}{clearbox}He already ran off, so isn't{nl}
that good enough?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ......{wait_fr:16}{nl}
Ah, sorry, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
I was lost in thought.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Kandori was pulling the{nl}
strings behind it all, huh.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
So, we're going to the{nl}
abandoned factory, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: This hospital has{nl}
such a bright atmosphere.{nl}
It's a relief.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Why does SEBEC have to{nl}
be under such tight security,{nl}
anyway?{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: I hear things are in{nl}
an uproar outside?{waitkey}If I weren't on duty, I'd go{nl}
have a look myself!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 800 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I'm a busy man. If{nl}
you've no business here,{nl}
off you go.{waitkey}{ret}
